268
00:14:20,181 --> 00:14:21,880
Tenanglah!

269
00:14:21,881 --> 00:14:23,180
Aku mengerti.

270
00:14:23,181 --> 00:14:25,580
Baik. Pertama-tama,

271
00:14:25,581 --> 00:14:27,880
