354
00:18:46,781 --> 00:18:52,481
dan bagiku untuk menyampaikan lokasinya via telepon.

355
00:18:55,581 --> 00:18:56,981
Maafkan aku.

356
00:18:58,281 --> 00:18:59,980
Petugas Takagi.

357
00:18:59,981 --> 00:19:04,581
Tapi kau mengerti, bukan?

358
00:19:07,481 --> 00:19:08,681
Bodoh.

359
00:19:11,281 --> 00:19:12,780
4 menit lagi!

