00:20:01,981 --> 00:20:03,280
Hei!

375
00:20:03,281 --> 00:20:04,980
Menghentikan bomnya!

376
00:20:04,981 --> 00:20:06,581
Hei! Tunggu!

377
00:20:17,281 --> 00:20:19,080
Polisi itu...

378
00:20:19,081 --> 00:20:23,280
